---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="首页" description="算电协同 · 电力交易 · 新能源 — 专业内容与投资分析">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-decor" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 260 260" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <circle cx="200" cy="60" r="80" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.3" />
        <circle cx="130" cy="130" r="100" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.2" />
        <path d="M60 200 Q 100 160 140 190 Q 180 220 220 180" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.25" fill="none" />
        <path d="M30 130 Q 80 100 130 120 Q 180 140 230 110" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.6" opacity="0.15" fill="none" />
        <circle cx="200" cy="60" r="3" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3" />
        <circle cx="140" cy="190" r="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.25" />
        <circle cx="230" cy="110" r="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-anim">算电协同 · 电力交易 · 新能源</h1>
      <div class="subtitle hero-anim">
        <strong>内容专注方向</strong> — 算力与电力协同、电力市场改革、新能源基础设施投资。
        记录专业思考，沉淀可复用框架。
      </div>
      <a href="/about" class="cta hero-anim">了解更多 →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>最新文章</h2>
    <ul class="article-card-grid">
      <li class="article-card featured">
        <span class="card-tag">算电协同</span>
        <a href="/blog/suan-dian-xie-tong-1" class="card-title">算电协同：为什么这是未来五年确定性很高的投资主题</a>
        <div class="card-desc">AI 算力集群用电已进入 500MW 级，算力正在成为新的电力需求。算电协同首次进入政府工作报告，政策窗口已经打开。</div>
        <div class="card-meta">2026-05 · 约 8 分钟阅读</div>
      </li>
      <li class="article-card">
        <span class="card-tag">算电协同</span>
        <a href="/blog/suan-dian-xie-tong-2" class="card-title">算电协同产业链拆解：利润池在哪里？</a>
        <div class="card-desc">上游绿电供给、中游智算基建、下游算力服务——三层的利润分布、竞争格局和卡位策略。</div>
        <div class="card-meta">2026-05 · 约 10 分钟阅读</div>
      </li>
      <li class="article-card">
        <span class="card-tag">投资方法论</span>
        <a href="/blog/impossible-triangle" class="card-title">不可能铁三角与战略分层定价：华为思路对投资的启示</a>
        <div class="card-desc">质量、成本、低价不可兼得。华为的解法不是三选二，而是市场分层——这对重卡充电站等基础设施投资同样适用。</div>
        <div class="card-meta">2026-05 · 约 5 分钟阅读</div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/gsap.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      if (typeof gsap !== 'undefined') {
        var heroEls = document.querySelectorAll('.hero-anim');
        if (heroEls.length) {
          gsap.from(heroEls, {
            y: 30,
            opacity: 0,
            duration: 0.7,
            ease: 'power3.out',
            stagger: 0.15
          });
        }
      }
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
<dcp-message-id>m0051</dcp-message-id>